<div class="dokuwiki export">



<h2><a name="abs" id="abs">abs</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

文法:

</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> 数値 <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>

abs()関数は、数値の絶対値を返します。
</p>

<p>
サンプル:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">     <span class="kw4">int</span> magic_number <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu0">10</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
     <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;推測してください: &quot;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
     cin <span class="sy0">&gt;&gt;</span> x<span class="sy0">;</span>
     <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;答えから &quot;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> magic_number <span class="sy0">-</span> x <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot; 離れています。&quot;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
C++では以下のようなオーバーロード版も提供されます:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> 数値 <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span> <span class="co1">// labs()と同じです</span>
&nbsp;
    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="co1">// 以下の関数はfabs()の別名です</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> 数値 <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> 数値 <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> 数値 <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
